text: Ronke Ademiluyi is a Nigerian fashion expert and entrepreneur. ==Life== A graduate of Law, Ademiluyi was born in England, United Kingdom, but she is a descent of Ile-Ife in Osun State, South-Western Nigeria. She is the founder of the Africa Fashion Week, a project that promotes African fashion designers through its subsidiaries, the Africa Fashion Week Nigeria and the Africa Fashion Week London. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Nigerian businesspeople Category:Nigerian fashion businesspeople Category:Yoruba women in business Category:Nigerian women lawyers Category:English people of Nigerian descent Category:English people of Yoruba descent Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
